title: “Beto days to come.” (LIVE from Austin)
description: America sends its best negotiator to denuclearize a dictator, and Democrats craft an economic message for 2018. Then Texas Democratic Senate candidate Beto O’Rourke joins Jon, Jon, Tommy, Dan, and Brittany on stage live at Austin City Limits.
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
